  "text": "In order to evaluate the VIP system performance and assess its image quality, the whole VIP geometry is simulated using the Geant4-based Architecture for Medicine-Oriented Simulations (GAMOS) [CITATION_1] . The Geant4 kernel provides the accurate simulation of particle interaction with the materials within the defined geometry.",
